Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是又不能中途退出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得很想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候奈亞子出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈亞子
